name: Cerestia Of Life - Last Origin
description:
First time making a LORA model after many experiments with bases, LR's and methods. This one turned out that is something I'm almost happy with and happy to share. It's probably a little overfitted but there is only so much artwork out there and i've tried to edit/decensor as much as I can to make a model from it.

It's based on Cerestia Of Life from Last Origin who is a rather large breasted elf, more info here: https://lastorigin.fandom.com/wiki/Cerestia

Trigger word is "cerestia_of_life" and use other trigger words such as breast_curtains & circlet or cow_outfit for her other outfit. Experiment with tags from the metadata to make her outfits more solid.

It has a mixture of SFW and NSFW images that it's trained on but more gearing towards NSFW given her outfits, so be warned.
